Speaker 1: Yeah. Yeah, that would be great.

Speaker 2: Okay. It's got AC339.

Speaker 1: Yeah, so – okay.

Speaker 2: So, yeah, you did receive the generic.

Speaker 1: I will send you out as a replacement, obviously, on us, because you already paid for it.

Speaker 2: The AGV.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Sorry about that.

Speaker 1: No, it happens. I understand. I thought maybe I screwed up.

Speaker 2: Yeah. No, you're fine.

Speaker 1: Yeah. No, you're fine.

Speaker 2: Okay, so we'll do 50 milligrams. We'll do 10 pills.

Speaker 1: Can I ship this to 601 Village Court, Traverse City, Michigan?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Correct, yes.

Speaker 1: All righty.

Speaker 2: You can't take these back, can you? I mean, because I've touched them now, so you can't –

Speaker 1: No.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: No, so you can just throw them away, keep them, whatever you want to do.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Yeah, and if you need anything in the future, we're always here at this phone number,

Speaker 2: Monday through Friday, 8 to 5 Pacific.

Speaker 1: And the way you will know that these are the AGV is on them, the pills will say 5-0 for 50.

Speaker 2: Right.

Speaker 1: And then – so the pills will say 5-0, and then the side of the bottle will say Greenstone,

Speaker 2: because that's the manufacturer.

Speaker 1: And as long as you take them on an empty stomach and you avoid alcohol the day you take them,

Speaker 2: you will definitely notice a significant improvement compared to regular Viagra.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: All right, I appreciate your help. Your name was what, Olivia, you said?

Speaker 1: Olivia, that's right.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: I appreciate your help very much. Thank you.

Speaker 1: Of course. Thank you so much, Randall. I hope you have a great day.

Speaker 2: You bet.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Thank you. You too. Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye.
